# Download Test Video Instructions

## Option 1: Use Your Own Video
Place your 1-minute security footage video here and rename it to: sample_security_clip.mp4

## Option 2: Download Sample Video
You can download a sample video for testing:

### Using PowerShell:
```powershell
# Navigate to the videos directory
cd "C:\Src\github\GemmaGuardian\src\MobileApp\app\src\main\assets\videos"

# Download a sample video (Big Buck Bunny - first 60 seconds)
Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://sample-videos.com/zip/10/mp4/SampleVideo_1280x720_1mb.mp4" -OutFile "sample_security_clip.mp4"
```

### Alternative Test Videos:
- https://file-examples.com/storage/fe86c7e5c66d4d93d32411f/2017/10/file_example_MP4_1280_10MG.mp4
- https://www.learningcontainer.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sample-mp4-file.mp4

## Requirements:
- Format: MP4 (recommended)
- Duration: Any length (player will handle it)
- Resolution: Any (1920x1080 recommended)
- Size: Keep under 10MB for smooth loading

## File Location:
This file should be replaced with an actual MP4 video file for the video player to work properly.
